query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND mi_idx.info > '8.0' AND n.gender in ('f') AND (n.name like '%W%') AND t.production_year < 2002 AND (t.title like '%mask%' OR t.title like '%treasure%') AND cct1.kind in ('crew','complete','complete+verified') AND (chn.name like '%Wonder Woman%' OR chn.name like '%Willy Wonka%' OR chn.name like '%The Joker%' OR chn.name like '%Katniss Everdeen%' OR chn.name like '%Forrest Gump%') AND it2.info in ('rentals','LD number of sides','LD supplement','adaption','LD analog left','runtimes','death date','LD frequency response','LD master format') AND (k.keyword like '%outlaw%' OR k.keyword like '%music%' OR k.keyword like '%revolution%') AND cct2.kind in ('crew','cast','complete')
